<% if @status == "accepted" %>
  Congratulations: your project proposal has been accepted. It is now on the
  public project list on the website, and students can apply to it. ...
<% elsif @status == "pending" %>
  Your project is still pending, and the administrators have decided that you
  must make the following changes to your proposal before it can be posted:
<% elsif @status == "rejected" %>
  The administrators have decided not to accept your project proposal. ...
<% end %>

<% if !@comments.blank? %>
  The administrators say:
  <%= @comments %>
<% end %>
